## Project Summary

# Karthik Koundinya - Personal Portfolio Website

This is a comprehensive, professional portfolio website showcasing Karthik Koundinya's work as an **AI Engineer & Full Stack Developer**. The portfolio demonstrates modern web development practices with a focus on performance, accessibility, and user experience.

