## üèóÔ∏è Architecture & Structure

### **Multi-Page Application**
- **Landing Page** (index.html) - Hero, about, featured skills/projects/experience, contact
- **Skills Page** (skills.html) - Comprehensive technical skills breakdown
- **Projects Page** (projects.html) - Detailed project portfolio (10+ projects)
- **Experience Page** (experience.html) - Professional work history  
